snippet.textDisplay: But really all these burgers suck. Except for Culvers, chain restaurants don't make good quality burgers. They mass produce them, they don't put the love and effort into making them like mom and pop joints do. When I'm in the mood for a burger, I go to one of the (many) local bars (and Culvers, if I haven't mentioned already) instead. Pub grub=best food. Support your local food joints, and I can also name all the great places in southern Wisconsin for ya!
